aving`，符合 DNS 故障的特征。\n\n### 分析结果\n- **根因假设**:\n  - **组件**: `checkoutservice`（调用方）\n  - **原因**: 由于 DNS 服务器 (`10.233.33.139:53`) 无法正确解析 `emailservice` 的域名，导致 `checkoutservice` 无法连接到 `emailservice`。\n  - **证据**: 日志中明确提到 DNS 查询失败 (`server misbehaving`)。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"dns\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"lookup\", \"server misbehaving\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"DNS 服务器无法解析 emailservice 的域名，导致连接失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n- 检查 DNS 服务器 (`10.233.33.139:53`) 的运行状态和配置。\n- 验证 `emailservice` 的域名是否正确注册到 DNS 服务器中。\n- 如果问题持续，可能需要排查网络或 DNS 服务的其他潜在问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"status_code 14: connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_avg_duration: 159703.05, anomaly_avg_duration: 2729809.45\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_avg_duration: 8686.46, anomaly_avg_duration: 291222.38\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_avg_duration: 1